123
00:13:57.560 --> 00:14:00.518
Telefonul a sunat
toata saptamana.

124
00:14:02.680 --> 00:14:06.309
Rosella aai tot spala camaile
ca sa aiba ceva de facut.

125
00:14:06.520 --> 00:14:09.318
