00:40:49.800 --> 00:40:51.472
Mulaumesc.

443
00:40:51.680 --> 00:40:54.194
Hei. asta e slujba mea.

444
00:40:54.400 --> 00:40:56.356
Bate palma!

445
00:40:59.720 --> 00:41:01.676
- Pa.
- Pa.

446
00:41:34.960 --> 00:41:37.554
- Buna. Eddie.
- Buna. Rachel.

447
00:41:37.760 --> 00:41:40.718
- Buna. Eddie.
- Ce bine sa va vad. d-le Turner.

448
00:41:54.480 --> 00:41:56.038
Frate!

449
00:41:57.600 --> 00:42:00.034
Aici e acasa.

